CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 10, 1970, pg. 15, reads: "Frogs Dinner - Dancing Party Sparks Holiday Season - Out-Going President - Dr. Eugene Youngue (right) offer some choice advice to new Frog president Dr. James Lewis who succeeded the psychiatrist. All Courier Photos by 'Teenie' Harris."
TitMainTitle: Dr. James Lewis and Dr. Eugene Youngue standing at microphone in Redwood Motor Hotel for FROGS Dinner - Dance party
